OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given longest
OL,4,Csentence yet over UK riots
OL,6,FAn arsonist who was involved in "one
OL,7,Fof the worst" cases of mob violence
OL,8,Fduring last month's riots has been
OL,9,Fgiven the longest sentence yet
OL,10,Frelating to the disorder.
OL,12,FThomas Birley, 27, fuelled a fire at a
OL,13,Fhotel housing asylum seekers in
OL,14,FRotherham, threw a bin at riot police
OL,15,Fand brandished a police baton during
OL,16,Ftrouble on 4 August.
OL,18,FHe was also part of a group which
OL,19,Fsmashed windows at the Holiday Inn
OL,20,FExpress.
