OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given longest
OL,4,Csentence yet over UK riots
OL,6,FBirley pleaded guilty to arson with
OL,7,Fintent to endanger life, which can
OL,8,Fcarry a life sentence, and also
OL,9,Fadmitted violent disorder and
OL,10,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
OL,12,FJailing him for nine years at
OL,13,FSheffield Crown Court, Judge Jeremy
OL,14,FRichardson KC said: "This case is
OL,15,Funquestionably one of the worst of the
OL,16,Fmany cases which have come before this
OL,17,Fcourt."
