OL,6,FHe said there was a "desire to
OL,7,Fperpetrate mob rule and commit very
OL,8,Fserious criminal offences in the
OL,9,Fprocess".
OL,11,F"From first to last, the venom of
OL,12,Fracism infected the entirety of what
OL,13,Foccurred," he said.
OL,15,FBirler was among hundreds of people
OL,16,Fwho gathered outside the hotel, where
OL,17,Faround 200 asylum seekers were
OL,18,Fstaying, in one of a series of anti-
OL,19,Fimmigration protests after the murders
OL,20,Fof three girls in Southport.
