OL,4,Csentence yet over UK riots
OL,6,FThe court was show CCTV of Birley, in
OL,7,Fa black hooded coat and red mask,
OL,8,Fputting wood on top of a fire that had
OL,9,Fbeen started when a bin was set alight
OL,10,Fin front of one of the doors of the
OL,11,Fhotel.
OL,13,FHe pulled down his mask to shout abuse
OL,14,Fat police.
OL,16,FThe court heard staff were taken into
OL,17,Fa panic room and barricaded themselves
OL,18,Fbehind fridges and freezers.
