OL,6,FMaintenance manager Paul Coulson said
OL,7,Fin a statement they were "scared to
OL,8,Fdeath" as they could smell smoke.
OL,10,FProsecutor Alisha Kaye said: "He
OL,11,Fdescribes how they thought they were
OL,12,Fgoing to burn to death."
OL,14,FBirley's defence barrister, Dermot
OL,15,FHughes, said the former painter and
OL,16,Fdecorator was "appalled" by his
OL,17,Factions.
OL,19,F"He expresses heartfelt remorse," Mr
OL,20,FHughes said.
