OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given longest
OL,4,Csentence yet over UK riots
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Andrew Knowles, of South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, said: "Birley
OL,8,Fclearly had the intent to cause harm
OL,9,Fand damage, and cared nothing for the
OL,10,Ffamilies, staff and police officers in
OL,11,Fthe hotel.
OL,13,F"This sentence does not reverse the
OL,14,Fphysical and psychological damage of
OL,15,Fthat day, but I know it will be
OL,16,Fwelcomed by the hotel workers,
OL,17,Fresidents who were in the hotel, and
OL,18,Fthe officers that were working that
OL,19,Fday."
